											p
												li
													| Sometimes the speaker goes out without her partner.
													br
													select(name='q2e')
														option(value='x')
															| Choose Answer
															option(value='1')
																| true
																option(value='2')
																	| false
													p
														li
															| The speaker thinks it is better if she and her partner go out together.
															br
